show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/8TYUEB
show.description: Trisha, a determined medical student, is desperately trying to save her ailing brother when a twist of fate changes everything. After accidentally spilling juice on Raghav — a wealthy and dangerous man — she finds herself cornered with two unsettling choices: work for him for two months or spend one night with him. Choosing the lesser evil, she opts for the job. But as she navigates Raghav's perilous world, unexpected emotions begin to surface. Just when it seems the real danger might be falling for him, Trisha discovers that the true threat lies much closer than she ever imagined.
